{"TopicId":110820,"ForumId":66,"TopicTitle":"Modding Monday: Engine Lighting","CreatedByName":"SQUAD","CreatedById":66485,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-25T21:02:00Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SQUAD","CreatedById":66485,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-25T21:02:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026lt;figure data-orig-width=\u0022480\u0022 data-orig-height=\u002292\u0022 class=\u0022tmblr-full\u0022\u0026gt;\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://36.media.tumblr.com/f877983c4f5dc185bb3b4a0e8611b711/tumblr_inline_nox6kviuPe1rr2wit_540.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022tumblr_inline_nox6kviuPe1rr2wit_540.jpg\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/figure\u0026gt;\u0026lt;figure data-orig-width=\u00221360\u0022 data-orig-height=\u0022768\u0022 class=\u0022tmblr-full\u0022\u0026gt;\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://41.media.tumblr.com/0e192b0e524983226b59a65f0f1bf57a/tumblr_inline_nox74kUEdK1rr2wit_540.png\u0022 alt=\u0022tumblr_inline_nox74kUEdK1rr2wit_540.png\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/figure\u0026gt;A simple mod that does exactly what it says on the tin: it adds a light source to every engine, and calculates the amount of light emitted based on the current thrust setting and the engine\u00C3\u00A2\u00E2\u201A\u00AC\u00E2\u201E\u00A2s power. The mod will work with both stock engines and those added by other mods.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\u00C3\u00A2\u00E2\u201A\u00AC\u00E2\u201E\u00A2s a small effect that really adds to the experience of night time launches and in-space burns. \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/121987-\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHead over to this thread\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E to download Engine lighting.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-05-25T21:18:45Z\u0022 title=\u002205/25/2015 09:18  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EMay 25, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by KasperVld\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"temporalExile","CreatedById":127675,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-25T21:51:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYes. All the yes. You now have no excuse to not use this in the Unity 5 update. Unless you do have one...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tajampi","CreatedById":74648,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-25T22:08:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks for the spotlight SQUAD! \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECheers! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LukeM","CreatedById":144906,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-25T23:55:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFun!!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jarmund","CreatedById":126888,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-26T00:04:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAwesome!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI can never seem to find a place for lamps on my landers, and for some reason, I always seem to end up on the dark side, especially if aerobraking is in the mix.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Yukon0009","CreatedById":109376,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-26T09:05:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ethank you tajampi \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ealso nice to have you back.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Leoworm","CreatedById":136802,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-26T09:52:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThis looks awesome \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-26T15:58:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYes, been using this one since it dropped. This is a great VFX mod that deserves the attention.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShadowZone","CreatedById":112420,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-26T18:12:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELooks great. Thanks for making me aware of this!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pslytely psycho","CreatedById":62775,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-27T09:59:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELike Chatterer, Planetshine, EVE, TAC, Dang it and a few others, this is a mod that adds something to the game I didn\u0027t even realize was missing until I installed it, now it is in the \u0027essential mod\u0027 list.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESuch a small change, such a large difference in appearance.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWell done!\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-05-27T10:02:08Z\u0022 title=\u002205/27/2015 10:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EMay 27, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by pslytely psycho\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}